name: city-of-ithaca-tax-parcels-for-tax-year-2000-cad-2000
notes: The active tax parcel boundaries in the City of Ithaca, organized by year. The data set includes previous lot lines (dashed consolidation lines), parcel connectors (z-hooks), parcel boundaries, printkey boundaries, deed boundaries, municipal boundaries, block boundaries, tax map boundaries, special district boundaries, and text layers for lot numbers, acreage, dimensions, etc.
